{"tid":668860,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★騰訊受累限韓令 大熱手遊《絕地求生》收入遇阻","createTime":"2018-05-18T03:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T05:12:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ff67a99b11dad06e6b7d40e39f29e467f973f9","tid":668860,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"騰訊業績展示手遊收入首季大增六成，投資者對騰訊手遊業績憂慮紓緩之際，《華爾街日報》報道，騰訊（00700）的兩款大熱手遊《絕地求生》在內地市場變現遇阻。<br />\n<br />\n報導指騰訊的兩款《絕地求生》手遊受內地制裁南韓影響，至今未獲官方審批出售遊戲內物品，騰訊股價今早一度由升轉跌。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述知情人士指，《絕地求生全軍出擊》、《絕地求生刺激戰場》 今年初在內地推出，可免費下載，但由於該兩款遊戲是從南韓遊戲開發商Bluehole獲得授權，但因中國正以薩德問題對南韓實施非正式制裁，現仍未獲監管機構批准銷售遊戲內物品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://invest.hket.com/article/2075852/%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E5%8F%97%E7%B4%AF%E9%99%90%E9%9F%93%E4%BB%A4%20%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1%E6%89%8B%E9%81%8A%E3%80%8A%E7%B5%95%E5%9C%B0%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E9%81%87%E9%98%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finvest.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2075852%2F%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E9%2599%2590%25E9%259F%2593%25E4%25BB%25A4%2520%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2586%25B1%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%2581%258A%25E3%2580%258A%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%2594%259F%25E3%2580%258B%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2581%2587%25E9%2598%25BB&d=4RKMSrBp3%2BDoZuM3FwVM1r%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=c673cd4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://invest.hket.com/article/2075852/%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E5%8F%97%E7%B4%AF%E9%99%90%E9%9F%93%E4%BB%A4%20%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1%E6%89%8B%E9%81%8A%E3%80%8A%E7%B5%95%E5%9C%B0%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E9%81%87%E9%98%BB</a>"},{"pid":"a8929b2712cdc85e8078865b06a6d00ab85b0a56","tid":668860,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"